cess=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rxn1665702770939.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rxn1665702770939.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rxn1665702770939.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rxn1665702770939\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">createOccurrence</code> method creates an occurrence.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__topic_d129200e1_d129201e1_d129202e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__p_d129203e1_d129204e1_d129205e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">import\n               com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__p_d129206e1_d129207e1_d129208e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">int createOccurrence (int</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">occNr</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__section_b5g_m4c_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d447950e73\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__p_d129212e1_d129213e1_d129214e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">occNr</var>—sequential number of the occurrence you want to create. If\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">occNr</var> is less than zero, the new occurrence is appended to the set\n            of occurrences. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">occNr</var> is less than or equal to the number of\n            occurrences plus one, the new occurrence is inserted in the specified location, moving\n            all higher numbered occurrences up by one.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__section_ays_n4c_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d447950e91\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__p_d129218e1_d129219e1_d129220e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">createOccurrence</code> method\n            returns the number of the new occurrence. The <code class=\"ph codeph\">createOccurrence</code> method\n            throws a UnifaceException if the occurrence number is out of range or zero (the Java\n            call-in does not support the concept of current occurrence).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__section_z2g_p4c_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d447950e106\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxn1665702770939__p_d129224e1_d129225e1_d129226e1\">The behavior of this method is equivalent to the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">creocc</span> ProcScript statement.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531837\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531837\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UnifaceEntity.createOccurrence Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The createOccurrence method creates an occurrence. import com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*; int createOccurrence (int occNr ) Parameters occNr —sequential number of the occurrence you want to create. If occNr is less than zero, the new occurrence is appended to the set of occurrences. If occNr is less than or equal to the number of occurrences plus one, the new occurrence is inserted in the specified location, moving all higher numbered occurrences up by one. Return Values The createOccurrence method returns the number of the new occurrence. The createOccurrence method throws a UnifaceException if the occurrence number is out of range or zero (the Java call-in does not support the concept of current occurrence). Description The behavior of this method is equivalent to the creocc ProcScript statement. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}